| Bias Awareness and Mitigation | 5            |  The tool offers customization options to adjust the tone and style of voiceovers, allowing users to mitigate potential biases and tailor the output to specific needs. Additionally, it avoids generating content that may be inflammatory or politically sensitive.                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
